@Barry Ancona I got it from the cross clues, but I didn’t understand it either. I had convinced myself that the clue referred to Manhattan, KS running a Union Pacific train station until 1990: <a href="https://www.preservemanhattan.org/projects.html" target="_blank">https://www.preservemanhattan.org/projects.html</a>

